column5: I was just curious about some of the other lakes that are near this area. We will be fishing the last week of May on Rainy, but I like to keep my options open. I cannot find the names of the lakes right now, but I kown there are a few in the area. Thanks for any info.

Lake Despair is right near Labelle's, then there the other lakes in the chain that are accessable from Despair, like Jackfish, Footprint and others. Then a little furthur drive west are Clearwater and Pipestone. Those are the main lakes nearby, don't know much about the area my self though.
